{{ instruction_screen_15 }}

Type 'ok' to confirm you have read and understood these instructions.

Please carefully read the following experiment instructions (page 16 of 17: Underestimate treatment charity payment detail: If guess is too low, charity receives a donation of a specified amount.).
{{ instruction_screen_16 }}

